curl -XPOST 'http://localhost:9200/electronic_products/_create/3638' -H 'Content-Type: application/json' -d '{"product_name": "SGM8422/SGM8424", "table_name": "TITLE", "content": "  SGM8422/SGM8424  2.4MHz, High Voltage, Rail-to-Rail  I/O Operational Amplifiers        SG Micro Corp  www.sg-micro.com  OCTOBER 2013 – REV. A. 2  "}'
curl -XPOST 'http://localhost:9200/electronic_products/_create/3639' -H 'Content-Type: application/json' -d '{"product_name": "SGM8422/SGM8424", "table_name": "GENERAL DESCRIPTION", "content": "GENERAL DESCRIPTION  The dual SGM8422 and quad SGM8424 are low power  operational amplifiers optimized for high voltage  systems. These devices can operate from 4.5V to 30V  single supply or from ±2.25V to ±15V dual power  supplies, and each amplifier consumes only 0.72mA  quiescent current. They support rail-to-rail input and  output operation, which results in wide dynamic range.  The SGM8422/4 are suitable for low power systems,  such as portable and battery-powered applications.  The SGM8422/4 have a gain-bandwidth product of  2.4MHz. They offer fast settling and slewing times.  These devices are well suited for TFT-LCDs.  The SGM8422 is available in Green SOIC-8 and  MSOP-8 packages. The SGM8424 is available in Green  TSSOP-14 and SOIC-14 packages. They are specified  over the extended -40℃ to +85℃ temperature range.  "}'
curl -XPOST 'http://localhost:9200/electronic_products/_create/3640' -H 'Content-Type: application/json' -d '{"product_name": "SGM8422/SGM8424", "table_name": "FEATURES", "content": "FEATURES  ● Rail-to-Rail Input and Output  ● Support Single or Dual Power Supplies:   4.5V to 30V or ±2.25V to ±15V  ● Gain-Bandwidth Product: 2.4MHz (TYP)  ● High Slew Rate: 2V/µs  ● Supply Current: 0.72mA/Amplifier  ● -40℃ to +85℃ Operating Temperature Range  ● Small Packaging:  SGM8422 Available in SOIC-8 and MSOP-8 Packages  SGM8424 Available in TSSOP-14 and SOIC-14   Packages      "}'
